This paper is likely to belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category as it discusses the brain and its structure. It also mentions the use of Hierarchical Temporal Memory (HTM), which is a machine learning algorithm inspired by the neocortex. The paper also touches on topics related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI), as well as systems and control (cs.SY) and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CC).
